00:11:27,853 --> 00:11:29,955
I think to really succeed, you
have to be really screwed up

271
00:11:29,989 --> 00:11:32,425
to be successful
in this business.

272
00:11:32,458 --> 00:11:35,327
- What did you
learn from Katharine Hepburn?

273
00:11:35,361 --> 00:11:38,164
What did you learn from
Hepburn in that movie?

