283
00:11:54,246 --> 00:11:56,082
She said, "Don't be theatrical."

284
00:11:56,115 --> 00:11:57,049
I said, "Well what do I do?"

285
00:11:57,083 --> 00:11:58,818
She said, "Speak the lines."

286
00:11:58,851 --> 00:12:02,188
Which sounds very simplistic,
but I think she was right.

287
00:12:04,824 --> 00:12:05,958
She's talking about filmmaking.

288
00:12:05,991 --> 00:12:07,126
Don't overact.

289
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,961
Don't show too much.

290
00:12:08,994 --> 00:12:12,832
