00:13:45,191 --> 00:13:47,293
James Cagney, and Marlon Brando.

337
00:13:49,195 --> 00:13:52,298
This chapter is undoubtedly
the most intense.

338
00:13:52,331 --> 00:13:54,633
Anthony Hopkins, still
grapples with a demon

