00:14:55,327 --> 00:14:58,097
which was a very
drastic thing to do.

359
00:14:59,198 --> 00:15:00,232
I hurt a few people,

360
00:15:03,736 --> 00:15:08,040
but it's the only way
I knew how to survive

361
00:15:08,073 --> 00:15:09,008
whatever I was going through.

362
00:15:09,041 --> 00:15:10,476
And so I got out.

363
00:15:10,509 --> 00:15:14,513
And I was in work, I started
work fairly soon after that.

