00:16:30,489 --> 00:16:32,725
most of my time now,

388
00:16:32,758 --> 00:16:36,228
It's that thing where it just
feels right inside, you know?

389
00:16:38,597 --> 00:16:40,032
No contention, no argument,

390
00:16:40,733 --> 00:16:44,136
no fighting, no belligerence.

