00:16:46,572 --> 00:16:49,842
- For him, California
becomes another planet,

392
00:16:49,875 --> 00:16:53,345
one on which he lives with his
second wife, Jennifer Lynton,

393
00:16:53,379 --> 00:16:55,447
who he met in England
while she was working

394
00:16:55,481 --> 00:16:57,182
as a production assistant.

395
00:16:59,418 --> 00:17:03,422
There, Anthony Hopkins left
his first wife Petronella,

396
00:17:03,455 --> 00:17:06,558
and the child they had
together, his daughter, Abigail.

397
00:17:08,727 --> 00:17:12,731
America for Hopkins is the
world of possibilities.

398
00:17:12,765 --> 00:17:16,335
Luck smiles on him, when in
'78, Richard Attenborough

399
00:17:16,368 --> 00:17:18,637
offers him a key
role in his career,

400
00:17:18,670 --> 00:17:22,541
as a mad ventriloquist in
the little known film, Magic.

401
00:17:22,574 --> 00:17:24,376
- You ruined the rising aces.

